gobblin.writer

Class FluentDataWriterBuilder<S,D,B extends FluentDataWriterBuilder<S,D,B>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • gobblin.writer.DataWriterBuilder<S,D>
      • gobblin.writer.FluentDataWriterBuilder<S,D,B>

  • public abstract class FluentDataWriterBuilder<S,D,B extends FluentDataWriterBuilder<S,D,B>>
extends DataWriterBuilder<S,D>
    A helper class to help create fluent DataWriterBuilders. To make the Java generics magic work, classes should declare their builders as MyDataWriterBuilder and use "return typedSelf()" instead of "return this" in their setters.
